headline: Ensign Group Shares Plunge 12% Despite Q4 Earnings Beat
summary: ENSG's fourth-quarter results gain on strong contribution from the Skilled Services unit, partly offset by the escalating cost of services. It estimates 2025 adjusted EPS to be within $6.16-$6.34.
